# Hidden video posts

When creating or editing hidden YouTube short transcript posts, follow `AGENTS.md` in the repo root.

Key rules:
- One git worktree per post (`hidden-post-<slug>` branch)
- Preview with `RBENV_VERSION=3.4.1 bundle exec jekyll serve --config _dev_config.yml --future`
- Do not commit until the author approves the preview
- Do not push or open a PR until explicitly asked
- PRs: `gh pr create --repo jtemporal/jtemporal.github.io`